videos.headline: T. Armstrong Jr. pass,to B. Reilly for 38 yds for a 1ST down

videos.headline: Armstrong's rushing TD gives Nebraska lead
videos.description: Nebraska QB Tommy Armstrong Jr. runs seven yards into the end zone for the touchdown giving the Cornhuskers an early lead over Wyoming.

videos.headline: Armstrong Jr. throws pick in red zone
videos.description: Nebraska QB Tommy Armstrong Jr. scrambles before throwing a pass that is intercepted by Wyoming's Andrew Wingard in the red zone.

videos.headline: Armstrong finds wide open receiver for 63-yard touchdown catch
videos.description: Nebraska QB Tommy Armstrong Jr. throws a pass complete to Alonzo Moore who finds wide open field and races for the 63-yard touchdown reception.

videos.headline: J. Allen pass,to T. Gentry for 31 yds for a 1ST down

videos.headline: Wyoming cuts deficit with great touchdown pass
videos.description: Wyoming QB Josh Allen scrambles out of the pocket and finds Tanner Gentry in the back corner of the end zone for a 35-yard touchdown reception to cut into their deficit against Nebraska.

videos.headline: Wyoming RB Brian Hill stiff arms Nebraska defender

videos.headline: Nebraska extends lead off tipped INT
videos.description: Nebraska safety Kieron Williams comes down with an interception and runs 23 yards down the field for the touchdown.

videos.headline: Armstrong floats pass 34 yards for TD
videos.description: Nebraska QB Tommy Armstrong Jr. finds Jordan Westerkamp for a 34-yard touchdown reception to extend the Cornhuskers lead over Wyoming.
